<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="hostel-hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Hostel Facilities</h1>
                <p>A safe, comfortable, and nurturing home away from home for our students.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="hostel-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>A Nurturing Environment for Growth and Learning</h2>
                <p>N.R.K. Public School offers well-maintained and secure hostel facilities for both boys and girls, providing a supportive environment conducive to academic success and personal development. Our hostel aims to be a home away from home, where students learn to live independently, cultivate friendships, and grow into responsible individuals under careful supervision.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="amenities-safety-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="card-row">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Comfortable Amenities</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>**Spacious Rooms:** Well-ventilated and furnished rooms with comfortable beds and study areas.</li>
                            <li>**Nutritious Meals:** A balanced and hygienic diet served in the dining hall, catering to student nutritional needs.</li>
                            <li>**Supervised Study Hours:** Dedicated time for supervised study to ensure academic progress.</li>
                            <li>**Recreation:** Common rooms with indoor games and outdoor play areas for relaxation.</li>
                            <li>**Medical Care:** First-aid facilities with a visiting doctor for routine health check-ups.</li>
                            <li>**Laundry Services:** Regular laundry services for students.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Safety and Supervision</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>**24/7 Security:** Round-the-clock security personnel and CCTV surveillance to ensure student safety.</li>
                            <li>**Experienced Wardens:** Dedicated and caring wardens who oversee the well-being and discipline of students.</li>
                            <li>**Strict Entry/Exit Protocols:** Controlled access to the hostel premises.</li>
                            <li>**Emergency Preparedness:** Clear emergency procedures and drills in place.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="daily-routine-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Typical Daily Routine</h2>
                <p>A structured daily routine helps students maintain discipline, focus on their studies, and develop healthy habits.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>**Morning:** Wake-up, freshen up, exercise/yoga, breakfast.</li>
                    <li>**Daytime:** School classes, lunch.</li>
                    <li>**Evening:** Supervised study hours, recreation time, dinner.</li>
                    <li>**Night:** Preparation for the next day, lights out.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Considering Hostel Life for Your Child?</h2>
                <p>Experience a disciplined and supportive environment at N.R.K. Public School hostel.</p>
                <a href="/school/contact" class="cta-button primary">Inquire About Hostel</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>